  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>Business travelers will welcome additional conveniences like the public computer with Internet access and access to copy and fax services.
All spacious guest rooms come equipped with microwaves, refrigerators, coffee makers, hair dryers, irons and ironing boards. Some rooms feature whirlpool bathtubs and desks. Non-smoking rooms are available.
Ample parking and valet cleaning services are offered on the premises for added guest convenience.
Offering a great location, terrific amenities and affordable rates, the Comfort Inn &amp; Suites hotel is the perfect place to stay on your next trip to Chatsworth.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The Comfort Inn &amp; Suites hotel is conveniently located near State Route 118, only one block from the Chatsworth Station transportation hub for Metrolink light rail service and more. This Chatsworth hotel is also close to California State University, Northridge (CSUN), the Ronald W. Reagan Presidential Library &amp; Museum and the San Fernando Mission, dating back to 1797.Additional nearby attractions less than 30 miles away include Universal Studios Hollywood theme park, Six Flags Magic Mountain amusement park and the Getty Center museum.
Shopping is abundant at several nearby malls, including the Northridge Shopping Center, Westfield Topanga and Westfield Promenade. A variety of entertainment venues, cocktail lounges and restaurants can be found in the surrounding area, including several within walking distance from this Chatsworth hotel.</Text>
  </Description>
